import React from 'react';
import { Container, TextField, Button, Typography, Box } from '@mui/material';

const LoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        minHeight: '100vh',
        display: 'flex',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5',
      }}
    >
      <Container
        maxWidth="sm"
        sx={{
          backgroundColor: 'white',
          padding: '2rem',
          borderRadius: '10px',
          boxShadow: '0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)',
        }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h4" align="center" gutterBottom>
          Login
        </Typography>
        <form>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            label="Username"
            margin="normal"
            variant="outlined"
          />
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            margin="normal"
            variant="outlined"
          />
          <Button
            fullWidth
            variant="contained"
            sx={{ mt: 2 }}
            type="submit"
            color="primary"
          >
            Login
          </Button>
        </form>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default LoginPage;
